column12: HANDHELD DRAIN CLEANING MACHINE WITH BIPOD SUPPORT
column13: A drain cleaning machine (1200) with a bipod support (1000) is described. The bipod support (1000) includes a base (1010), two legs (1020,1040), a retaining member (1060), and a latch (1080). The retaining member (1060) and latch (1080) are configured to engage and secure the drain cleaning machine (1200) to the bipod support (1000). The bipod support (1000) enables rocking movement of the drain cleaning machine (1200) while supporting the weight of the machine. Also described are related methods of use of the bipod support (1000) with the drain cleaning machine (1200).

column12: BIPOD SUPPORT FOR HANDHELD DRAIN CLEANING MACHINE
column13: A bipod support for a drain cleaning machine is described. The bipod support includes a base, a plurality of legs, a retaining member, and a latch. The retaining member and latch are configured to engage and secure the drain cleaning machine to the bipod support. The bipod support enables rocking movement of the drain cleaning machine while supporting the weight of the machine. Also described are related methods of use of the bipod support.
